data.description: Experience mid-century charm that is turnkey just in time for the holidays! Immerse yourself in the 3D tour of this classic revival with custom-stained heart pine hardwood floors, and an open air floorplan featuring a giant wood-framed window that fills the space with natural light. The kitchen features boho lighting, ample natural wood cabinets, and a custom stone-coat countertop. Paint, flooring, fixtures and ceilings renewed in October 2023. Discover the bonus space beyond the side entry: with a large ensuite bath, walk-in closet, and private entrance - it may be your ideal owner's suite, guest quarters, game room, or studio! The backyard features a large open patio surrounded by manicured mature trees, and space for a dog run or food garden. Extra parking with a swing drive, two-car carport, and a practical storage shed. Close to Arlington entertainment district, DFW Airport, UT, and easy access to I-20 or I-30.
